<title>Apr_1993: Re: Original sin vs. universal sin</title>
<h1>Re: Original sin vs. universal sin</h1>
Dan Blake (<i>dblake@hprnd.rose.hp.com</i>)<br>
<i>Tue, 20 Apr 93 23:46:41 PDT</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#348">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#348">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#348">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#348">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0349.html">PHTH1@cc.newcastle.edu.au: "Evil &amp; guilt"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0347.html">Juha Helminen: "Re: Col 2:16 Any good explanation?"</a>
