<title>Apr_1993: re:SDA Plants and Music</title>
<h1>re:SDA Plants and Music</h1>
Ray Mialki (<i>rm1g+@andrew.cmu.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Wed, 21 Apr 1993 18:05:11 -0400 (EDT)</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#359">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#359">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#359">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#359">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0360.html">Michael Nickless: "Re: The $100 Million Question"</a>
