<h1>Re:  Stars in my Crown</h1>
Marcus Stringer (<i>marcuss@microsoft.com</i>)<br>
<i>Wed, 21 Apr 93 22:22:07 PDT</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#374">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#374">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#374">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#374">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0375.html">Steven Timm: "The Ruben Conspiracy"</a>
