<title>Apr_1993: Re: SDA-   Plants and Music</title>
<h1>Re: SDA-   Plants and Music</h1>
Ruben Gonzalez (<i>ruben@ee.uts.edu.au</i>)<br>
<i>Fri, 23 Apr 93 11:55:48 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#371">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#371">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#371">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#371">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
