<title>Apr_1993: soy sauce and b-12</title>
<h1>soy sauce and b-12</h1>
<i>AAGAARD%morekypr.BITNET@bitnet.cc.cmu.edu</i><br>
<i>24 Apr 1993 16:36:32 -0400 (EDT)</i>
