they start with alt.sex, will they later decide to ban alt.vampyres or <br>
alt.pagan, too.  I admit some of it is morally incorrect, but I figure <br>
we're old enough now to make decisions on what we read.<br>
I also think that some of the newsgroups allow us to learn about the <br>
views of others(example: alt.atheism, or will that one be next on the <br>
chopping block.)<br>
