<title>Apr_1993: Re: Original sin (and guilt)</title>
<h1>Re: Original sin (and guilt)</h1>
Sherman Cox (<i>scox@uahcs2.cs.uah.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Thu, 29 Apr 93 8:51:17 CDT</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#441">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#441">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#441">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#441">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0442.html">Fred Christiansen: "Re: PROOF BY CAPS LOCK and other mysteries of email"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0440.html">Woody Baker: "Re: Church clothes"</a>
