<title>Apr_1993: Re: Stars in My Crown</title>
<h1>Re: Stars in My Crown</h1>
Dan Drazen (<i>drazen@edmund.cs.andrews.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Thu, 29 Apr 1993 08:17:19 -0400 (EDT)</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#431">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#431">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#431">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#431">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0432.html">Sherman Cox: "Re: Original sin (and guilt)"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0430.html">Sherman Cox: "Re: Original sin (and guilt)"</a>
<li> <b>In reply to:</b> <a href="0422.html">Steven Timm: "Re: Stars in My Crown"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
