If and when Union goes on Internet this will be an issue that will be<br>
needed to be dealt with.  At first maybe al will be sent through.. who<br>
knows.  But if it is decided to cut Alt.Sex and other Alt.* gropus then<br>
how do you cut the line?  Who can make the decition?  Would Song of<br>
