rec.basket weaving because I don't like it? NO.  As a student I do not<br>
have a maniging word on this. But as a student and advacate of internet I<br>
say to let it be and for students to use their heads.<br>
<p>
If Alt.* is cut all a student needs to do is telnet to nyx or some other<br>
public site and read them there.  It would be pointless to block them if<br>
thoguht control is the issue.<br>
