<title>Apr_1993: Re: WWC and Internet News</title>
<h1>Re: WWC and Internet News</h1>
Fred Christiansen (<i>fredch@quad4.phx.mcd.mot.com</i>)<br>
<i>Fri, 30 Apr 93 10:44:56 MST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#444">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#444">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#444">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#444">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0445.html">Steven Timm: "Sodom and Gomorrah"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0443.html">Steven Timm: "Has anyone heard of NLP?"</a>
<li> <b>In reply to:</b> <a href="0427.html">Healy, Tammy R: "Re: WWC and Internet News"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
<li> <b>Next in thread:</b> <a href="0429.html">Alan Fargusson: "Re: WWC and Internet News"</a>
