Hi all,<br>
<p>
   I'm a rather passive member of SDAnet, and usually just enjoy listening<br>
to all of the goings on.  This afternoon, some friends came over and we<br>
were discussing all sorts of things and I thought I'd throw this out to <br>
the net.<br>
<p>
   Has anyone heard of NLP (Neural-Linguistic Programming)?  I've just<br>
heard a bit about it and would like to know if any of you have more <br>
information about it?  <br>
<p>
--John (jash@eecs.wsu.edu)<br>
KB7ONG<br>
[We had a good discussion on this once but it has been a while.  I <br>
