<title>Apr_1993: RE: Immunity to the Gospel?</title>
<h1>RE: Immunity to the Gospel?</h1>
Marcus Stringer (<i>marcuss@microsoft.com</i>)<br>
<i>Wed, 12 May 93 09:33:28 PDT</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#223">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#223">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#223">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#223">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0224.html">ELAINE KENNEDY: "DINOSAURS"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0222.html">Vice-Dean Jerry Wiley - x06473: "Re:  Center Stage ..."</a>
