<title>Mar_1992: NLP and baptism</title>
<h1>NLP and baptism</h1>
McCluskey G (<i>glenm@usl.com</i>)<br>
<i>Tue, 3 Mar 92 15:06:22 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#21">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#21">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#21">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#21">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0022.html">Cheryl Berthelsen: "Manipulating people to become members?"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0020.html">Paul Gates: "Re: Majoring in Minors"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
<li> <b>Next in thread:</b> <a href="0027.html">Glen Pringle: "Re: NLP and baptism"</a>
