<title>Mar_1992: Dr. Loveless and new forms of prayer</title>
<h1>Dr. Loveless and new forms of prayer</h1>
Dwain E. Woode (<i>dwoode@aramis.cs.ua.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Mon, 9 Mar 92 21:50:59 -0600</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#41">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#41">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#41">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#41">[ author ]</a>
