<title>Mar_1992: Re: Am I a Modern Johah?</title>
<h1>Re: Am I a Modern Johah?</h1>
Dave Buxton (<i>davidbu@loowit.wr.tek.com</i>)<br>
<i>Tue, 10 Mar 92 09:16:11 PST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#42">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#42">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#42">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#42">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0043.html">Nancy Vyhmeister: "Re: Jonah"</a>
