<i>&gt; [ministry vs engineering dilemma]</i><br>
<i>&gt; . . . .</i><br>
<i>&gt; 	During the spring quarter of my junior year, I changed my major to</i><br>
<i>&gt; Computer Science.  I finished in May of 1991 and am presently a Ph.D</i><br>
