<title>Mar_1992: Dr. Loveless and new forms of prayer</title>
<h1>Dr. Loveless and new forms of prayer</h1>
Dave (<i>st0o+%ANDREW.CMU.EDU%CMU.EDU@bitnet.cc.cmu.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Mon, 9 Mar 1992 15:27:26 -0500</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#55">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#55">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#55">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#55">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0056.html">Alice Fay Martin: "SDA subculture"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0054.html">Steven Timm: "Re: Defining Catholic vs Protestant"</a>
