I believe the reason why we SDAs are placed in the Pentecostal category be <br>
some other Christians is that we teach about the gifts of the Holy Spirit, <br>
especially the gift of prophecy. To some that makes us Pentecostal. It has <br>
nothing to do with worship style as was suggested. I have been to pentecostal <br>
churches that make SDA churches look alive.<br>
<p>
Ed, Compuserve 72450,2430<br>
