      This is another SDA question from a Non-SDA..<br>
      I have picked up on the net some discussions on witnessing<br>
      and evangelism.  Do any SDA churches do any "door to door"<br>
      evangelism ?  At this time, I don't have any strong convictions<br>
      either way regarding door to door, but am just curious.  Also,<br>
      are there any certain formats for alter calls ? Does every church<br>
      use them, or only some?  Is it at every service or only from time<br>
      to time ?<br>
      Thanks in advance<br>
      Eric<br>
      Hershey, Pa.<br>
<!-- body="end" -->
