<title>Mar_1992: CIA and SDA</title>
<h1>CIA and SDA</h1>
Danny Kumamoto (<i>kumamoto@verisys.slb.com</i>)<br>
<i>Thu, 26 Mar 92 09:32:58 JST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#79">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#79">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#79">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#79">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0080.html">McCluskey G: "life and death"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0078.html">Steven Timm: "SDA Race Relations"</a>
