<title>Mar_1992: 1992 Youth Evangelism International Workshop</title>
<h1>1992 Youth Evangelism International Workshop</h1>
Steven Timm (<i>st0o+@andrew.cmu.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Sat, 28 Mar 1992 19:13:24 -0500 (EST)</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#82">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#82">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#82">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#82">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0083.html">Nancy Vyhmeister: "Re: South Africa votes"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0081.html">Steven Timm: "Time magazine February 24, 1992"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
</ul>
<!-- body="start" -->
A brochure that came with my latest issue of Dialogue gives the <br>
following information:<br>
<p>
1992 Youth Evangelism Workshop,<br>
Prague, Czechoslovakia, August 4-8, 1992.<br>
To directly follow the youth congress in Budapest, Hungary, July 27-August 1.<br>
<p>
The workshop will be held at the University of Agriculture in Prague.<br>
Anyone with an interest in Youth or Campus ministry, or youth themselves,<br>
may attend.  The workshop fee is $140.00 US, and lodging is $100.00 double<br>
occupancy, $150.00 single occupancy.<br>
<p>
Speakers read like a who's who of youth workers.<br>
Bailey Gillespie, D. Wong, B. Muganda, M. Ryan, D. Hitchcock, R. Gibbs,<br>
W. Scragg, D. Baker, W. Johnsson, T. Neslund, R. Barron, S. Case, D. Case,<br>
M. Stevenson, D. Neal, R. Osborne, H. Rasi, N. Bassham, H. Berg, E. DeLeon,<br>
A. Marenko, E. Osei, D. Duerksen, J. Carter, M. Allen, R. Holbrook, M. Allen,<br>
B. Gane, D. Harris, R. Folkenberg.<br>
<p>
I know I will be in Europe for at least a month this summer on business,<br>
and it seems worthwhile to try to arrange it during this time.  If <br>
others have more information on this seminar, let us know.<br>
<p>
Steve Timm<br>
<!-- body="end" -->
