On the question of race relations in the SDA Church, I have found two very<br>
interesting books:<br>
<p>
Graybill, Ronald.  E. G. White and Church Race Relations.  Washington, DC:<br>
     Review and Herald, 1970.<br>
<p>
     Graybill, Ronald.  Mission to Black America.  Mtn. View, CA:<br>
	Pacific Press, 1971.<br>
<p>
	Very informative and well written.<br>
<p>
	Nancy Vyhmeister<br>
