<title>Dec_1992: Re: principles of interpretation</title>
<h1>Re: principles of interpretation</h1>
Paul Gates (<i>72450.2430@compuserve.com</i>)<br>
<i>02 Dec 92 22:11:17 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#12">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#12">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#12">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#12">[ author ]</a>
