<title>Dec_1992: Bible Search Software</title>
<h1>Bible Search Software</h1>
Fred Christiansen (<i>fredch@phx.mcd.mot.com</i>)<br>
<i>Wed, 2 Dec 92 13:20:10 MST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#16">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#16">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#16">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#16">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
