and that everything outside of the 27 fundamentals are basically<br>
curiosities of Adventism and not to be taken too seriously.  He said<br>
that a big problem he has with the independents is that they continue<br>
to try to bring to importance those theological issues that are not<br>
part of the 27.<br>
