<title>Dec_1992: Re: Chew Gum (Chiclets) in the Church...</title>
<h1>Re: Chew Gum (Chiclets) in the Church...</h1>
Ruben Gonzalez (<i>ruben@ee.uts.edu.au</i>)<br>
<i>Fri, 11 Dec 92 13:10:02 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#72">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#72">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#72">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#72">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0073.html">TANG BENG YONG: "Re:  Chew Gum (Chiclets) in the Church..."</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0071.html">Paul Gates: "Independent Ministries"</a>
