<!-- body="start" -->
Plenary evening sessions are by John Kent, missionary in Papua New Guinea;<br>
Lawrence Burns; Tony Campolo; Eugene Hsu, China; Patricia Gustin, former<br>
single missionary to Thailand.  New Year's Even includes a party, a concert,<br>
and a commitment service.<br>
<p>
Morning seminars are on "Mission explorers" or "How to adopt a people group."<br>
P.M. Seminars are on people groups, world regions, methods of evangelism,<br>
North American mission, institutional ministry, personal spirituality, and<br>
mission practice.  There are as many as 12 groups under each seminar slot.<br>
<p>
Finally, there are some 20 exhibitors, both from the organized SDA Church<br>
and supporting ministries.<br>
<p>
The first meeting is at 7 p.m. December 27.  The whole thing ends with the<br>
new year's commitment service.<br>
