<i>&gt; </i><br>
<i>&gt; All sins are equal in the eyes of God,</i><br>
<i>&gt; </i><br>
<i>&gt; Steve Timm</i><br>
------------<br>
<p>
Steve, you say this as if it were axiomatic.  I don't think it<br>
is.  There are many accounts within the Bible that indicate<br>
that God judges sin for the particular sin that it is, not just<br>
the fact that it is a sin.  Proverbs singles out many sins for<br>
specific condemnation.<br>
<p>
Dan Blake<br>
