<title>Dec_1992: Merry Christmas and Happy New Year</title>
<h1>Merry Christmas and Happy New Year</h1>
Steven Timm (<i>st0o+@andrew.cmu.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Sun, 20 Dec 1992 22:01:32 -0500 (EST)</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#100">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#100">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#100">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#100">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0101.html">TANG BENG YONG: "Re:  Talking heads"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0099.html">Steven Timm: "Financial status and mixed blessings"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
