25 minute offering calls ? !!!<br>
I wonder if people would feel like giving more if the offering call was shortened or done away with. It sounds like a pity if the memberss are willing to<br>
give only after a 25 minute appeal. I thought that the offering during the<br>
service was supposed to be an act of worship. We should follow the example<br>
of the poor widdow who gave her meagre mite to the temple without the priests,<br>
pharisees or whoever, having to make extenuated pleas for offerings.<br>
- Beng Tang<br>
