Hi all,<br>
<p>
<p>
	I would like to strongly recommend that people who email private<br>
replies regarding questions being discussed publically on SDAnet<br>
do not necessarily wish to be responded to via public posts.<br>
<p>
	I think that this is a matter of ethics. I believe<br>
(and I think Steve would agree with me) that SDAnet is not for personal<br>
reply neither for observations regarding one's person. Rather for<br>
public discussion of matters of public interest.<br>
<p>
Ruben.<br>
	<br>
[I certainly do agree with Ruben.  If I have been guilty of such,<br>
I apologize in advance, but please bring to my attention.  SCT]<br>
