 <br>
I'm just wondering if anyone is interested in just helping out with the<br>
network a bit.  All that is involved is to keep track of people on the<br>
list, try to encourage people to use the list and try to get some good<br>
postings to the list, and help out in any problems that people seem to<br>
have.  I will be moving at the end of May and I don't think I'll be able<br>
to get networking access wherever I end up.  As I don't usually handle<br>
the problems but rather divert them to my brother, whoever wishes to<br>
take on the job may or may not be involved with the problems.<br>
