so I'm going to try to reintroduce myself, because I noticed that I don't have<br>
any details with my name and email address which were printed with the last<br>
directory.<br>
 <br>
I'm Jerome Grimmer, a senior in Electrical Engineering at Southern Illinois Uni<br>
-versity at Carbondale, Carbondale, Illinois.  I'm very interested in computers<br>
and also seem to be the only SDA at SIUC that has bothered to get any sort of<br>
network access. :(  There are more of us here at SIU, but since they don't have<br>
mainframe accounts, they don't have network access and consequently don't know<br>
about SDA-L.  But that's beside the point.  Other interests include photo-<br>
graphy, bicycling, and of course prayer.  Hopefully next time the directory<br>
comes out this info will be added to it.<br>
 <br>
I also have an internet address (this same account) and it is ST6267@siucvmb.si<br>
u.edu, so you Internet folks can reach me at it instead of going over our slow<br>
BITnet link.  I tried to sub this account via Internet and got a message back<br>
from the Listserv saying that the list was locked, so could somebody please<br>
sub me to it via Internet and set my BITnet subscription to NOMAIL?  Thanks.<br>
 <br>
Jerome Grimmer<br>
Bitnet: ST6267@SIUCVMB<br>
Internet: st6267@siucvmb.siu.edu<br>
