<p>
We are beginning to look forward to our trip in April and May. Evelyn<br>
and I will be in Dayton, OH the last week end of April for the Dayton<br>
Hamfest!! They usually have close to 30,000 Amateurs and /or Computer<br>
enthusiasts. The Adventist "Hams" in the area prepare special services<br>
for us too. We usually have a potluck together on Sabbath at one of the<br>
churches. From there we will motor down to Burleson, TX to spend about<br>
4 days with our son and his family.<br>
<p>
This next Sabbath at Cambridge, MD church Gary Ross from the GC will be<br>
our speaker for church. After potluck we will have a Religous Liberty<br>
Rally with several of the neighboring SDA churches coming in.<br>
<p>
&lt;&lt;Paul&gt;&gt;<br>
<!-- body="end" -->
