<title>Feb_1992: Re: congregationalism</title>
<h1>Re: congregationalism</h1>
Paul Gates (<i>70516.420@compuserve.com</i>)<br>
<i>28 Feb 92 18:41:50 EST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#121">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#121">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#121">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#121">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0122.html">Paul Gates: "Re: Congregationalism"</a>
