A few days ago, someone posted a derogatory statement against American's<br>
United for Separation of Chuirch and state.  It seemed to imply that they<br>
were a greater  danger to Religious Liberty than Jerry Falwell.  Also  this<br>
post seemed to attack the principle of Separation of Church and State.<br>
<p>
No one questioned him.  I must be completely out of touch for I am a member<br>
of that organization and I do believe in the principle of Separation.<br>
<p>
I would like to hear other views.  Also I would like to get the name<br>
and state of the Adventist Congressman.  What are his views on separation.<br>
I know he is Republican.<br>
