<title>Feb_1993: faculty position</title>
<h1>faculty position</h1>
Lawrence Turner (<i>turner@edmund.cs.andrews.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Mon, 1 Feb 1993 18:24:01 -0500 (EST)</i>
<p>
<ul>
