Steve<br>
<p>
I would appreciate it if you would post the following on the net.<br>
<p>
<p>
The department of Computer Science and Information Systems at Andrews<br>
University has a tenure track faculty position available for the<br>
the 1993-94 academic year.  <br>
<p>
The candidate that we are looking for is an individual dedicated to<br>
Christian education.  A Ph.D. (or close to finishing) in the general<br>
area of Software Engineering is preferred; however, a Ph.D. in a<br>
related are with experience in data base systems, software engineering<br>
methodology, or similar areas would be considered.<br>
<p>
The faculty member would be expected to teach undergraduate and graduate<br>
courses in her or his area of expertise.  Research is encouraged, <br>
especially research that would involved students.<br>
<p>
Please send a resume and information to:  Lawrence E. Turner, Jr.<br>
<pre>
