<title>Feb_1993: Re: Thoughts on Bible Translations</title>
<h1>Re: Thoughts on Bible Translations</h1>
Steven Timm (<i>st0o+@andrew.cmu.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Tue,  2 Feb 1993 00:10:23 -0500 (EST)</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#14">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#14">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#14">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#14">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0015.html">Steven Timm: "Updated directory"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0013.html">Ruben Gonzalez: "Thoughts on Bible Translations"</a>
<li> <b>In reply to:</b> <a href="0013.html">Ruben Gonzalez: "Thoughts on Bible Translations"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
<li> <b>Next in thread:</b> <a href="0016.html">Steven Timm: "Re: Thoughts on Bible Translations"</a>
