<title>Feb_1993: More on Bible translations</title>
<h1>More on Bible translations</h1>
Steven Timm (<i>st0o+@andrew.cmu.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Wed,  3 Feb 1993 10:58:54 -0500 (EST)</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#23">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#23">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#23">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#23">[ author ]</a>
<!-- next="start" -->
<li> <b>Next message:</b> <a href="0024.html">GRUMLING DENNIS : "KJV"</a>
<li> <b>Previous message:</b> <a href="0022.html">Russell Yonkers: "How about a new more acurate translation then"</a>
<!-- nextthread="start" -->
