<title>Feb_1993: Re: Copyrighting means "not inspired?"</title>
<h1>Re: Copyrighting means "not inspired?"</h1>
Scott  Bechtel (<i>srbechte@nyx.cs.du.edu</i>)<br>
<i>Wed, 3 Feb 93 18:40:05 MST</i>
<p>
<ul>
<li> <b>Messages sorted by:</b> <a href="date.html#30">[ date ]</a><a href="index.html#30">[ thread ]</a><a href="subject.html#30">[ subject ]</a><a href="author.html#30">[ author ]</a>
