*Message-id: &lt;01GGTFWIQJIO8WWKQD@UCBEH.SAN.UC.EDU&gt;<br>
<p>
This  message  was  originally  submitted by  friedmn@NOVAVAX.NOVA.EDU  to  the<br>
RESPONSE list at NDSUVM1. If you simply forward it back to the list, it will be<br>
distributed with the paragraph you are now reading being automatically removed.<br>
If you  edit the  contributions you  receive into  a digest,  you will  need to<br>
remove this  paragraph before mailing the  result to the list.  Finally, if you<br>
need more information from the author of this message, you should be able to do<br>
