<p>
Columbia MM has *two* methods of forwarding messages:<br>
<p>
FORWARD (which merely sends the body of the mail but makes completely new<br>
headers)<br>
<p>
REMAIL which adds the "Resent-from" headers, &amp;c.<br>
<p>
(Columbia MM is for Un*x systems.)<br>
