     about Link Hudson's questions, I'll send you some stuff on it.<br>
Meanwhile, check out these very good booklets:<br>
<p>
PROPHET OF THE END; by Vance Ferrell;<br>
Copyright 1984; Pilgrim's Books, Altamont, TN 37301<br>
- very good, written for non SDAs too, has many examples<br>
of fulfilled prophecies etc, eg. the 1906 San Francisco<br>
earthquake.<br>
<p>
