Copyright 1983; Review &amp; Herald Pub. Assn.<br>
- a small booklet with interesting info about Ellen White's<br>
life, calling and work.<br>
<p>
Ellen G. White and the Seventh-day Adventist Church;<br>
by D. A. Delafield; c. 1963, Pacific Press Pub. Assn.<br>
- similar to the previous work.<br>
<p>
     You might be able to get them from ABC or the VOP, thats where<br>
I got mine.<br>
     Actually, if Mr. Hudson is really interested in E G White and<br>
the gift of prophecy, it might be a good chance to give him these<br>
booklets, so that he can know more about it and the SDA church.<br>
