Iron and clay...let's see...<br>
<p>
Serbs &amp; Croatians?<br>
Muslims &amp; Christians?<br>
Neo-Nazis &amp; Eastern refugees?<br>
Irish catholics &amp; Irish protestants?<br>
Arabs &amp; Jews?<br>
<p>
Prophecy or no prophecy, any Earthly power trying to unite Europe, be it<br>
economically, politically or whatever, is up against it. Makes me wonder<br>
how the Romans did it in the first place!<br>
