I FEEL THAT ADVENTISTS HAVE NOT ONLY THE RIGHT, BUT THE RESPONSIBILTY TO BE IN POSITIONS OF POWER. UNFORTUNATELY, THERE HAS COME A<br>
MINDSET INTO THE CHURCH THAT GOVERNMENT IS EVIL; THAT WE SHOULD REFRAIN FROMPOLITCAL ACTIVITIES EXCEPT THOSE THAT WOULD BE CONSIDERED<br>
AS LOBBYING FOR OUR RIGHTS. I RECENTLY HEARD A SERMON THAT WAS DELIVERED BY OUR PASTOR ON "RELIGIOUS LIBERTY" THAT WAS DEFINITELY<br>
TAINTED WITH THAT MINDSET. HE WAS SUBJECTING THE CONGREGATION TO DISINFORMATION THAT WAS DISSEMINATED BY THE PEOPLE FOR THE AMERICAN<br>
WAY -- OOPS! I'M SORRY -- AMERICANS UNITED FOR SEPARATION OF CHURCH AND STATE. TO ALL OF YOU UNBELIEVERS IN THE TRUTH OF JUDICIAL RESTRAINT<br>
AND ORIGINAL CONSTITUTIONAL INTENT, THE JUDICIAL ACTIVISM THAT CAME UP WITH THE CONVOLUTED CONCEPT OF THE "WALL OF SEPARATION" IS OF MORE<br>
DANGER TO OUR RELIGIOUS LIBERTY THAN JERRY FALLWELL COULD EVER BE. GETTING BACK TO MY POINT OF EVIL GOVERNMENT -- GOVERNMENTS ARE AMORAL<br>
INSTITUTIONS AND REFLECT THE VALUES OF THE PEOPLE SERVING IN OFFICE. I AM HAPPY TO POINT OUT THAT HERE IN MARYLAND WE ELECTED A SDA<br>
CONGRESSMAN (CONSERVATIVE REPUBLICAN, PRAISE THE LORD) TO CONGRESS BY THE NAME OF ROSCOE BARTLETT. IT IS MY UNDERSTANDING THAT HE IS<br>
THE THIRD SDA IN CONGRESS IN HISTORY. I PLAN TO BE THE FOURTH. THOSE WHO WOULD DISAGREE WITH OUR PARTICIPATION IN POLITICS SHOULD<br>
ASK THEMSELVES HOW THE JEWISH NATION WOULD HAVE GOTTEN ALONG WITHOUT HIGHLY PLACED PEOPLE LIKE DANIEL OR ESTHER.<br>
JUST ONE NOTE IN CLOSING, THOUGH. I AM DISAPPOINTED IN MY FELLOW BRETHEN ALIGNING HIMSELF WITH THE LIBERTINE PARTY. I DON'T FEEL THAT<br>
LEGALIZING NARCOTICS, PROSTITUTION, AND OTHER SUCH OUTRAGEOUS ACTIVITIES SHOULD BE A GOOD PLATFORM FOR AN ADVENTIST TO RUN ON.<br>
<p>
SINCERELY,<br>
MARK BILBY<br>
<!-- body="end" -->
